---
title: Fresh Tagliatelle in Creamy Bacon Sauce with Peas, Rocket and Balsamic Drizzle
description: This Fresh Tagliatelle in Creamy Bacon Sauce is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF221216_R40_W04_UK_F11648-6_KB_Main__Tagliatelle_edit_low-950d44e4.jpg
